rows.label: bf08310100_0002
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*gasp*

rows.label: bf08310100_0004
rows.name: The Great Void... It's almost completely gone...

rows.label: bf08310100_0006
rows.name: After all, the Great Void was Serpent's doing.

rows.label: bf08310100_0008
rows.name: Yes, indeed.

rows.label: bf08310100_0010
rows.name:
So with Serpent gone, the Great Void
could not support itself...

rows.label: bf08310100_0012
rows.name:
If only we were above the surface,
we could easily cross.

rows.label: bf08310100_0014
rows.name: I mean, it doesn't look impossible to climb...

rows.label: bf08310100_0020
rows.name: But it's nastier than any mountain, that's for sure.

rows.label: bf08310100_0030
rows.name: Everyone! Here!

rows.label: bf08310100_0040
rows.name: Homura?

rows.label: bf08310100_0050
rows.name:
The insides of the World Tree... I'd never have
thought...

rows.label: bf08310100_0060
rows.name:
It seems to be an artificial tower
enveloped by gargantuan plant life.

rows.label: bf08310100_0070
rows.name: It seems like we can use this to travel up.

rows.label: bf08310100_0080
rows.name:
Up? Homura...
What did you do?

rows.label: bf08310100_0090
rows.name: Honestly, I'm not sure myself.

rows.label: bf08310100_0100
rows.name: It's like my body is remembering something all by itself.

rows.label: bf08310100_0110
rows.name:
It must be...another power granted to
the Master Blade by Father...

rows.label: bf08310100_0120
rows.name: So...we need to hurry.

rows.label: bf08310100_0130
rows.name: Homura...

rows.label: bf08310100_0140
rows.name:
This was hardwired into my brain.
So, Metsu must have the same thing.

rows.label: bf08310100_0150
rows.name: Metsu too...

rows.label: bf08310100_0160
rows.name: Seems this is some kind of elevator.

rows.label: bf08310100_0170
rows.name: That's some fancy glazing...

rows.label: bf08310100_0180
rows.name:
Ooh, you never were good with heights.
Shut your eyes!

rows.label: bf08310100_0190
rows.name: Let's go.
